data.description: Historic Wimberley home that was estimated to be built in the early 1940's in downtown Wimberley. This property features a 3 bed/2 bath home full of character. From the custom natural wood kitchen to the full blower fireplace system. The property sits on 1.18 acres and has a 1920 sqft pole barn workshop. There is high speed internet through Spectrum and house is on Wimberley Water. The zoning on this property is NS so commercial use is acceptable. Conditional Use Permit is also in place at this time.Restrictions: Yes
